data.description: Beautiful Estate on almost an acre lot backing to wooded private land. Located in the coveted Lakeside School District and just a few minutes from Lake Catherine! Light and bright with soaring ceilings and lovely millwork throughout! Primary suite with a spa-styled bathroom with large separate vanities and sleek walk-in shower. Elegant 1.5 story foyer with beautiful entry. As you enter, you see a Grand Open concept Living Room, two Gourmet Islands, Kitchen open to Family Room and a stairway leading to the 2nd floor Bonus Room.
